headline: 3 Reasons to Buy DexCom Stock Like There's No Tomorrow
summary: Medical device specialist DexCom (NASDAQ: DXCM) is going through a rough patch.  The company's shares are down sharply year to date due to unimpressive financial results -- and some of the headwinds it has encountered are, no doubt, concerning.  The company's slower-than-expected growth in international markets in the second quarter comes to mind.
